abstract: MATAMOROS, Mexico, Jan. 23.--A strong body of Indians have been murdering and robbing people in the vicinity of Hermosillo. Four Customs guards and 20 ranchmen pursued them yesterday. Several of the ranchmen were wounded, but none killed. Eleven soldiers in Guadalajara yesterday murdered the guard and deserted.
